<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>AI Supercycle Investment Quant Strategy</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, monospace; background: #0a0e17; color: #e0e6ed; line-height: 1.5; }
    .container { max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    h1 { font-size: 1.6rem; color: #60efff; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; color: #8ba4d0; margin: 20px 0 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #1e2a3a; padding-bottom: 6px; }
    h3 { font-size: 1rem; color: #6db3ff; margin: 10px 0; }
    .subtitle { color: #6b7f99; font-size: 0.85rem; margin-bottom: 20px; }

    /* Language Toggle */
    .lang-toggle { display: inline-flex; gap: 2px; border: 1px solid #334155; border-radius: 6px; overflow: hidden; }
    .lang-btn { padding: 4px 10px; border: none; cursor: pointer; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; background: #1e293b; color: #94a3b8; transition: all 0.2s; }
    .lang-btn:hover { background: #334155; color: #e0e6ed; }
    .lang-btn.active { background: #2563eb; color: #fff; }

    .controls { display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 16px; align-items: center; }
    .btn { padding: 8px 18px; border: none; border-radius: 6px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; transition: all 0.2s; }
    .btn-primary { background: #2563eb; color: #fff; }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: #3b82f6; }
    .btn-success { background: #059669; color: #fff; }
    .btn-success:hover { background: #10b981; }
    .btn-danger { background: #dc2626; color: #fff; }
    .btn-danger:hover { background: #ef4444; }
    .btn-warning { background: #d97706; color: #fff; }
    .btn-warning:hover { background: #f59e0b; }
    .btn-outline { background: transparent; border: 1px solid #334155; color: #94a3b8; }
    .btn-outline:hover { background: #1e293b; }
    .btn-sm { padding: 4px 10px; font-size: 0.75rem; }
    select { padding: 8px 12px; border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid #334155; background: #1e293b; color: #e0e6ed; font-size: 0.85rem; }
    input[type="text"], input[type="password"] { padding: 8px 12px; border-radius: 6px; border: 1px solid #334155; background: #1e293b; color: #e0e6ed; font-size: 0.85rem; width: 250px; }
    label { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #94a3b8; }

    .card { background: #111827; border: 1px solid #1e2a3a; border-radius: 10px; padding: 16px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .card-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .grid { display: grid; gap: 12px; }
    .grid-2 { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .grid-3 { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
    .grid-4 { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); }

    table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.8rem; }
    th { background: #1e293b; color: #94a3b8; padding: 8px 10px; text-align: left; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }
    td { padding: 8px 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #1e2a3a; }
    tr:hover td { background: #1a2332; }
    .table-wrapper { overflow-x: auto; max-height: 500px; overflow-y: auto; }

    .badge { display: inline-block; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; }
    .badge-layer1 { background: #7c3aed20; color: #a78bfa; border: 1px solid #7c3aed40; }
    .badge-layer2 { background: #2563eb20; color: #60a5fa; border: 1px solid #2563eb40; }
    .badge-layer3 { background: #05966920; color: #34d399; border: 1px solid #05966940; }
    .badge-layer4 { background: #d9770620; color: #fbbf24; border: 1px solid #d9770640; }
    .badge-buy { background: #05966920; color: #34d399; }
    .badge-hold { background: #d9770620; color: #fbbf24; }
    .badge-sell { background: #dc262620; color: #f87171; }
    .badge-strong { background: #05966930; color: #6ee7b7; font-weight: bold; }
    .badge-kr { background: #c2410c20; color: #fb923c; border: 1px solid #c2410c40; }
    .badge-us { background: #2563eb20; color: #93c5fd; border: 1px solid #2563eb40; }

    .metric { text-align: center; }
    .metric-value { font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 700; color: #60efff; }
    .metric-label { font-size: 0.7rem; color: #64748b; text-transform: uppercase; }

    .scenario-tabs { display: flex; gap: 6px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .scenario-tab { padding: 8px 16px; border: 1px solid #334155; border-radius: 6px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 0.8rem; background: #1e293b; color: #94a3b8; transition: all 0.2s; }
    .scenario-tab:hover { background: #334155; color: #e0e6ed; }
    .scenario-tab.active { background: #2563eb; color: #fff; border-color: #2563eb; }
    .scenario-content { display: none; }
    .scenario-content.active { display: block; }

    .loading { text-align: center; padding: 40px; color: #64748b; }
    .spinner { border: 3px solid #1e293b; border-top: 3px solid #2563eb; border-radius: 50%; width: 30px; height: 30px; animation: spin 0.8s linear infinite; margin: 0 auto 12px; }
    @keyframes spin { to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }

    .alert { padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: 6px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 0.8rem; }
    .alert-info { background: #2563eb20; color: #93c5fd; border: 1px solid #2563eb40; }
    .alert-warning { background: #d9770620; color: #fde68a; border: 1px solid #d9770640; }
    .alert-error { background: #dc262620; color: #fca5a5; border: 1px solid #dc262640; }

    footer { text-align: center; padding: 30px; color: #475569; font-size: 0.75rem; border-top: 1px solid #1e2a3a; margin-top: 40px; }
    .status-dot { width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%; display: inline-block; margin-right: 6px; }
    .status-online { background: #34d399; }
    .status-offline { background: #f87171; }
    .status-pending { background: #fbbf24; }
    .row-top { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; gap: 16px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row-top">
      <div>
        <h1 id="titleMain">AI Supercycle Investment Quant Strategy</h1>
        <div class="subtitle">
          <span class="status-dot status-pending" id="statusDot"></span>
          <span id="statusText">초기화 중...</span> &nbsp;|&nbsp;
          <span id="llmStatusText" style="color:#fbbf24;">LLM 연결 전 (Rule-Based 엔진)</span> &nbsp;|&nbsp;
          <span id="langTagline">Node.js + TypeScript</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="lang-toggle" id="langToggle">
        <button class="lang-btn active" onclick="setLang('ko')">한국어</button>
        <button class="lang-btn" onclick="setLang('en')">English</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- API Key Notice -->
    <div class="alert alert-info" id="apiNotice" style="display:none;margin-bottom:12px;"></div>

    <!-- Controls -->
    <div class="controls">
      <select id="llmProvider">
        <option value="rule-based" data-ko="규칙 기반 엔진 (API 키 불필요)" data-en="Rule-Based Engine (No API Key)">규칙 기반 엔진 (API 키 불필요)</option>
        <option value="claude">Claude (Anthropic)</option>
        <option value="deepseek">DeepSeek</option>
      </select>
      <input type="password" id="apiKey" placeholder="API Key" style="width:300px;flex-shrink:0;" oninput="updateLlmStatus()" autocomplete="off" spellcheck="false">
      <button class="btn btn-primary" onclick="refreshData()" id="btnRefresh">데이터 갱신</button>
      <button class="btn btn-warning" onclick="runLLMAnalysis()" id="btnLLM">LLM 분석</button>
      <button class="btn btn-outline" onclick="loadAll()" id="btnLoad">전체 로드</button>
    </div>

    <!-- LLM Output -->
    <div id="llmOutput" style="display:none;">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header"><h3 id="hLLM">LLM 분석 결과</h3><button class="btn btn-sm btn-outline" onclick="document.getElementById('llmOutput').style.display='none'">✕</button></div>
        <div id="llmContent"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Summary Metrics -->
    <div class="grid grid-4" id="summaryMetrics" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
      <div class="card metric"><div class="metric-value" id="metricCount">-</div><div class="metric-label" id="lblCount">추적 종목</div></div>
      <div class="card metric"><div class="metric-value" id="metricAvgScore">-</div><div class="metric-label" id="lblAvgScore">평균 점수</div></div>
      <div class="card metric"><div class="metric-value" id="metricReturn">-</div><div class="metric-label" id="lblReturn">예상 수익률 12M</div></div>
      <div class="card metric"><div class="metric-value" id="metricHbmPhase">-</div><div class="metric-label" id="lblHbmPhase">HBM 사이클</div></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Scored Stocks Table -->
    <h2 id="hRankings">AI 슈퍼사이클 종목 랭킹 (4-Layer 모델)</h2>
    <div class="table-wrapper" id="stocksTable"><div class="loading"><div class="spinner"></div><span id="tLoadingStocks">종목 데이터 로딩 중...</span></div></div>

    <!-- Strategy Comparison: Conservative → Destructive -->
    <h2 id="hScenarios">투자 패턴 & 종목 구성: 보수 → 파괴</h2>
    <div id="strategyComparison" style="margin-bottom:20px;"><div class="loading"><div class="spinner"></div><span id="tLoadingCorr">전략 비교 로딩 중...</span></div></div>

    <!-- Investment Scenarios (detail view) -->
    <h2 id="hScenarioDetail">리스크 프로필별 상세 전략</h2>
    <div class="scenario-tabs" id="scenarioTabs">
      <div class="scenario-tab" onclick="switchScenario('conservative')"><span data-ko="보수 (Conservative)" data-en="Conservative (보수)">보수 (Conservative)</span></div>
      <div class="scenario-tab" onclick="switchScenario('moderate')"><span data-ko="중도 (Moderate)" data-en="Moderate (중도)">중도 (Moderate)</span></div>
      <div class="scenario-tab" onclick="switchScenario('aggressive')"><span data-ko="공격 (Aggressive)" data-en="Aggressive (공격)">공격 (Aggressive)</span></div>
      <div class="scenario-tab active" onclick="switchScenario('destructive')"><span data-ko="파괴 (Destructive)" data-en="Destructive (파괴)">파괴 (Destructive)</span></div>
    </div>

    <div id="scenarioPanels">
      <div class="scenario-content" id="scenario-conservative"><div class="loading"><div class="spinner"></div><span id="tLoadingScenario">전략 로딩 중...</span></div></div>
      <div class="scenario-content" id="scenario-moderate"><div class="loading"><div class="spinner"></div><span id="tLoadingScenario2">전략 로딩 중...</span></div></div>
      <div class="scenario-content" id="scenario-aggressive"><div class="loading"><div class="spinner"></div><span id="tLoadingScenario3">전략 로딩 중...</span></div></div>
      <div class="scenario-content active" id="scenario-destructive"><div class="loading"><div class="spinner"></div><span id="tLoadingScenario4">전략 로딩 중...</span></div></div>
    </div>
    <!-- Recommended Portfolio Outlook -->
    <h2 id="hPortfolio">추천 포트폴리오: 1개월 / 3개월 / 12개월 전망</h2>
    <div id="portfolioPanel"><div class="loading"><div class="spinner"></div><span>포트폴리오 전망 계산 중...</span></div></div>

    <footer id="footerText">
      AI Super Cycle Quant Strategy v2.0 · Based on vibe-investing by Dennis Kim (gameworkerkim) · MIT License<br>
      교육/연구 목적의 시뮬레이션입니다. 실제 투자 권유가 아닙니다.
    </footer>
  </div>

